@startuml 07_PersistenceFlow
!theme plain
title Ruffnova - 数据持久化时序图

participant "AppState" as State
participant "SettingsPersistence\n(UserDefaults)" as Settings
participant "LibraryService" as LibSvc
participant "LibraryPersistence" as LibPersist
participant "CollectionService" as CollSvc
participant "BookmarkManager" as BookMgr
participant "ThumbnailService" as ThumbSvc
participant "GameStorageService" as GameStorage
participant "PermissionPolicyService" as PermSvc
participant "Disk\n(~/Library/Application Support/RuffleFlashPlayer/)" as Disk

== 设置持久化 (Combine 自动保存) ==

State -> State : setupPersistence()
note over State
  Combine $property.sink 订阅:
  - quality → settings.quality
  - volume → settings.volume
  - isMuted → settings.isMuted
  - playbackSpeed → settings.speed
  - isLooping → settings.isLooping
  - showDebugUI → settings.showDebugUI
  - maxExecutionDuration → settings.maxExecution
  - quality → bridge.setQuality()
  - volume → bridge.setVolume()
  ...
end note

State -> Settings : save via @Published sink
Settings -> Disk : UserDefaults\n(standard plist)

== 库数据持久化 ==

State -> LibSvc : add(item)
activate LibSvc
LibSvc -> LibSvc : dedup by resolved URL
LibSvc -> LibSvc : create bookmark data\nURL.bookmarkData()
LibSvc -> Disk : library.json\n{version: 3, items: [...]}
deactivate LibSvc

State -> LibSvc : update(item) { changes }
LibSvc -> LibSvc : mutate item fields
LibSvc -> Disk : library.json (overwrite)

== 每文件播放偏好 ==

note over State
  每次用户更改播放设置时:
  volume/mute/quality/speed/loop/mode
  → LibraryService.update(item) {
      playbackPreferences = PlaybackPreferences(...)
    }
end note

State -> LibSvc : update preferences
LibSvc -> Disk : library.json\n(per-item PlaybackPreferences)

== 缩略图存储 ==

State -> ThumbSvc : captureThumbnail()
State -> State : grab Metal drawable\nCGImage crop/scale
State -> ThumbSvc : store(image, for: identifier)
activate ThumbSvc
ThumbSvc -> ThumbSvc : CGImageSource validate
ThumbSvc -> Disk : Thumbnails/{uuid}.png
ThumbSvc --> State : identifier string
deactivate ThumbSvc

State -> LibSvc : update(item) { thumbnailIdentifier }

== 收藏夹持久化 ==

State -> BookMgr : toggleFavorite(for: url)
activate BookMgr
BookMgr -> BookMgr : add/remove Bookmark
BookMgr -> Disk : bookmarks.json
deactivate BookMgr

== 集合持久化 ==

State -> CollSvc : create/rename/delete/add/remove
activate CollSvc
CollSvc -> Disk : collections.json\n{collections: [{id, name, itemIDs, ...}]}
deactivate CollSvc

== Flash SharedObject 存储 ==

State -> GameStorage : read/replace/delete
activate GameStorage
GameStorage -> GameStorage : ruffle_storage_* FFI calls
GameStorage -> Disk : SharedObjects/{library-uuid}/{name}.sol
deactivate GameStorage

== 权限策略持久化 ==

State -> PermSvc : apply(.allowForFile, ...)
activate PermSvc
PermSvc -> PermSvc : save override to store
PermSvc -> Disk : permissionPolicies.json\n{version, overrides: [...]}
deactivate PermSvc

== 文件路径汇总 ==

note over Disk
  **~/Library/Application Support/RuffleFlashPlayer/**

  library.json          - 库条目 (含元数据、偏好、书签)
  collections.json      - 用户集合
  bookmarks.json        - 收藏夹
  recentFiles.json      - 最近文件 (遗留, 迁移后保留)
  permissionPolicies.json - 权限覆盖
  Thumbnails/{uuid}.png - 缩略图
  SharedObjects/{uuid}/{name}.sol - Flash LSO 存储

  **UserDefaults (系统 plist):**
  quality, volume, isMuted, isLooping, speed,
  showDebugUI, showToolbar, maxExecutionDuration,
  letterbox, autoplay, defaultPlayerMode, appLanguage
end note

@enduml
